# Three-Address Code (TAC) - Optimized

 1: FUNC_BEGIN Master
 2: DECL int sum
 3: sum = 0
 4: DECL int n
 5: n = 1
 6: t1 = 1
 7: sum = 1
 8: t2 = 2
 9: n = 2
10: PRINT 1
11: DECL int outer
12: outer = 1
13: DECL int inner
14: inner = 1
15: PRINT 1
16: t5 = 2
17: inner = 2
18: t6 = 2
19: outer = 2
20: FUNC_END Master
